This paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT) sub-category as it deals with the transmission of information over a communication channel. Additionally, it may also belong to the Networked Systems (cs.NI) sub-category as it involves the transmission of signals over a network. Other possible sub-categories include Optics (cs.OH) as it deals with optical transmission systems, Performance Analysis (cs.PF) as it evaluates the performance of the transmission system, and Programming Languages (cs.PL) as it may involve programming and implementation of the transmission system.
